entry.title: SociaPol-Development/Contracts
entry.summary: Sociapol is a virtual gaming and socialization platform or Metaverse that closely resembles the real world. It enables users to develop their surroundings, socialize with other users, create and monetize immersive gaming experiences, and share and earn rewards for creative content—all of this using the platform’s native utility token, SPOL.
